node.title: Person seriously injured, Armed Offenders Squad at Nelson property
node.description: A person is understood to have been seriously injured at a house in central Nelson.
node.content:
["A person is understood to have been seriously injured at a house in central Nelson.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Claire Eastham-Farrelly\n
", "Police were called to the Washington Road address after 1pm today, after reports a person had been injured.", "The Armed Offenders Squad are also at the scene as a precaution.", "St John are also at the scene, but details of injuries are not yet known."]
